7 An Act relating to the True Grit Trail; directing the
Oklahoma Department of Transportation to erect
8 signage in certain locations; requiring the Oklahoma
Department of Transportation to collaborate with the
9 Oklahoma Tourism and Recreation Department to
maintain certain online resources for the True Grit
10 Trail; providing source of funding; providing for
codification; and providing an effective date.
