14 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
15 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
16 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 4101 of Title 69, unless there
17 is created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
18 The Oklahoma Department of Transportation shall erect signage
19 designating the following roads as the True Grit Trail:
20 Beginning at the start, US Highway 64 at the Oklahoma state line
21 with Arkansas to US Highway 59. From US Highway 59 to US Highway
22 271. From US Highway 271 to the town of Spiro, Oklahoma. From
23 Spiro Oklahoma back to US 59. From US Highway 59 to Oklahoma
24 Highway 31. From Oklahoma Highway 31 to US Highway 270. From US
