1 High way 270 to Mains Street in McAlester. From Main Street to East
2 Krebs Avenue. From East Krebs Avenue and Main Street back to US
3 Highway 27O. From US Highway 270 to Oklahoma Highway 2. From
4 Oklahoma Highway 2 to Robbers Cave State Park. From Robbers Cave
5 State Park on Oklahoma Highway 2 to US Highway 270. From US Highway
6 270 to Oklahoma Highway 82. From Oklahoma Highway 82 to US Highway
7 27A. From US Highway 271 to Oklahoma Highway 1. From Oklahoma
8 Highway 1 and ending at the intersection of Oklahoma Highway 1 and
9 US Highway 259.
10 B. The Oklahoma Department of Transportation shall erect
11 informational highway signage designed or approved by the Oklahoma
12 Tourism and Recreation Department to direct visitors to sites of
13 significant interest along the True Grit Trail, including:
14 1. The City of Sallisaw;
15 2. The Town of Spiro;
16 3. The Town of Bokoshe;
17 4. The Town of McCurtain;
18 5. The Town of Kinta;
19 6. The Town of Quinton;
20 7. The City of Krebs;
21 8. The City of McAlester;
22 9. The City of Hartshorne;
23 10. The City of Wilburton;
24 11. Robbers Cave State Park;
